g":"黑鬼：琴晚你明明話唔好提個衰佬"},{"pid":"1419455a98d14757e8917e87b2109e2b03f34050","tid":2035434,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"侵侵都係剩係識得口交<br />\n被人玩到無晒face<br />\n算把啦"},{"pid":"7d5b02a3e848c2ab81eb153d25dd065df483137d","tid":2035434,"uid":63029,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9bf4da8513ae04be77f510feff218a54a437c27b","tid":2035434,"uid":119596,"like":45,"dislike":18,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"不得不說維尼由一個副市長做上去都好好野, 佢老婆都好識揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"全靠佢努力賺嗰8萬，再加老豆嗰5百萬，佢終於買到林寶堅尼喇"},{"pid":"58d660b67c4eb9dcda9704acc77fba4322f35c35","tid":2035434,"uid":29649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"875bed0f47f288b88f50ffa35536ee98959dfd2a","tid":2035434,"uid":301299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c814287d32a58076d3ad0e3d66f5c87e7a81308d","tid":2035434,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4899/4899123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4899%2F4899123.jpg&h=c62f8d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自WHO官網）<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（COVID-19）重創全球，最早爆發疫情的中國及世界衛生組織（WHO）都備受指責。外媒披露，中國國家主席習近平的妻子彭麗媛與賴比瑞亞前總統瑟利夫（Ellen Johnson Sirleaf）、英超足球隊利物浦（Liverpool）門將貝克（Alisson Becker）同列世衛9名親善大使之一，官網卻對她的身分隻字未提。<br />\n<br />\n根據世衛官網，WHO於2011年6月3日任命彭麗媛為結核病及愛滋病防治親善大使（Goodwill Ambassador for Tuberculosis and HIV/AIDS）。此前，她2006年1月成為中國愛滋病毒預防大使，2007年3月起擔任國家結核病控制及預防大使。<br />\n<br />\nWHO網站上的人物介紹中寫道，彭麗媛是中國著名女高音歌唱家及演員，也是中國人民解放軍總政治部歌舞團團長，在公務員中排名第一，軍階為少將，稱她為衛生及控制結核病及愛滋的堅定倡導者，2011年任命時更盛讚她擁有「聞名世界的嗓音與同情心」、「是一顆閃亮的星，擁有眾多受人尊敬的崇拜者」。<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》報導，彭麗媛早在1987年就嫁給時任廣東省廈門副市長的習近平，2011年由當時的WHO秘書長陳馮富珍（Margaret Chan）任命為親善大使。現任世衛總秘書長譚德塞接任後，重新任命彭麗媛擔任組織一員，但官網至今未提她是習近平的妻子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200526/1722558.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200526%2F1722558.htm&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=c7cd467e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200526/1722558.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"廣東省廈門市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"唔係福建嫁咩"},{"pid":"ebb6060e4b9a8bd8276f87c983f54e1dcceed4ad","tid":2035434,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"ed5a1965221a8f3a30152df3716edabd908627c6","tid":2035434,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6064764836a5dc8953af12080c278bdeaec0316a","tid":2035434,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"who真係越做越肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95902d544e64eedc6435a3141086af4e98317b71","tid":2035434,"uid":148053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"有無人可以改左林奠同习豬篇潮文，變佢同咸濕菜"},{"pid":"d49aa7caed32408d597ab90149764d84b87dca0b","tid":2035434,"uid":20368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"有咩好提<br />\n係人都知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befe4c99a9af17ca16547a7f0e85985f06b6e346","tid":2035434,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3d08cef7f458e27e91b58eb4e21945a6e0c991be","tid":2035434,"uid":134683,"like":0,"